---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="min-h-[85vh] flex items-center pt-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-24">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-center md:items-start">
        <!-- Profile Image -->
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 reveal">
          <div class="w-28 h-28 md:w-36 md:h-36 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden ring-1 ring-stone-200 dark:ring-stone-800 hover:ring-accent-400/40 dark:hover:ring-accent-500/30 transition-all duration-500">
            <img
              src="/profile.jpg"
              alt="Daisy Xinlei Lin"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Text Content -->
        <div>
          <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-50 mb-3 reveal delay-1">
            Daisy Xinlei Lin
          </h1>
          <p class="text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400 mb-8 reveal delay-2">
            Research Scientist &amp; Engineer &mdash; Amazon AGI SF Lab
          </p>
          <div class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 leading-relaxed max-w-xl space-y-4 mb-10 reveal delay-3">
            <p>
              I work on RL post-training for AI agents. At Amazon AGI SF Lab, I worked on the end-to-end RL training recipe for <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/aws/build-reliable-ai-agents-for-ui-workflow-automation-with-amazon-nova-act-now-generally-available/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-200 underline decoration-stone-300 dark:decoration-stone-700 underline-offset-[3px] hover:decoration-accent-400 transition-colors duration-300">Nova Act</a> &mdash; Amazon's production browser-use agent &mdash; and build evaluation frameworks for agentic systems.
            </p>
            <p>
              My PhD at NYU was about how humans plan and learn: I ran large-scale experiments to understand what makes people get better at complex tasks, and how that compares to AI.
            </p>
            <p>
              I think AI should be humans' thought partners &mdash; adapting to collaborate with us better and better. I also think they should be beautiful.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-6 reveal delay-4">
            <a href="/lab/" class="btn-primary group">
              Interactive Lab
              <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a href="#featured" class="text-sm text-stone-500 hover:text-stone-900 dark:hover:text-stone-200 link-underline transition-colors duration-300">
              Research
            </a>
            <a href="#contact" class="text-sm text-stone-500 hover:text-stone-900 dark:hover:text-stone-200 link-underline transition-colors duration-300">
              Contact
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured Work Section -->
  <section id="featured" class="py-20 border-t border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="section-label mb-12 reveal">Featured Work</h2>

      <!-- Industry Experience -->
      <div class="mb-16 reveal">
        <h3 class="section-label mb-8 !text-stone-300 dark:!text-stone-600">Industry</h3>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800 p-6 md:p-8 hover:border-stone-300 dark:hover:border-stone-700 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <h4 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">Amazon Nova Act</h4>
            <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-0.5 bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-950/50 text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 rounded-full border border-emerald-200 dark:border-emerald-500/20">Production</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 mb-5 leading-relaxed">
            Owned the end-to-end RL training recipe for Nova Act. Designed and shipped an online data curator that improved RL sample efficiency. Diagnosed and resolved a training/inference mismatch that stabilized RL training at scale across agentic tasks. Drove measurable gains in training data diversity and reliability.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-5">
            <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 bg-stone-100 dark:bg-stone-800/50 text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400 rounded-full">Reinforcement Learning</span>
            <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 bg-stone-100 dark:bg-stone-800/50 text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400 rounded-full">Computer Use</span>
            <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 bg-stone-100 dark:bg-stone-800/50 text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400 rounded-full">LLM Post-Training</span>
          </div>
          <a
            href="https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/aws/build-reliable-ai-agents-for-ui-workflow-automation-with-amazon-nova-act-now-generally-available/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400 hover:text-accent-700 dark:hover:text-accent-300 transition-colors duration-300 group"
          >
            Read AWS Blog Post
            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Selected Publications -->
      <div class="reveal">
        <h3 class="section-label mb-8 !text-stone-300 dark:!text-stone-600">Selected Publications</h3>

        <div class="space-y-1">

          <article class="group -mx-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-stone-100/60 dark:hover:bg-stone-900/50 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-1 sm:gap-3 mb-1">
              <h4 class="font-serif text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 group-hover:text-accent-700 dark:group-hover:text-accent-400 transition-colors duration-300">Diagnosing Component-Level Failures in Computer-Use Agents</h4>
              <span class="text-xs text-stone-400 dark:text-stone-500 whitespace-nowrap">COLM 2026 (In review)</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-500">Tianchen Guan, Daisy Xinlei Lin, Xiangjun Wang, Shuyan Zhou</p>
          </article>

          <article class="group -mx-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-stone-100/60 dark:hover:bg-stone-900/50 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-1 sm:gap-3 mb-1">
              <h4 class="font-serif text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 group-hover:text-accent-700 dark:group-hover:text-accent-400 transition-colors duration-300">Limitations in Planning Ability in AlphaZero</h4>
              <span class="text-xs text-stone-400 dark:text-stone-500 whitespace-nowrap">NeurIPS 2024</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 mb-2">Daisy Xinlei Lin, Brenden Lake, Wei Ji Ma</p>
            <a href="https://openreview.net/forum?id=ZAbYb4jDJt" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400 hover:text-accent-700 dark:hover:text-accent-300 transition-colors duration-300">
              Paper
              <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg>
            </a>
          </article>

          <article class="group -mx-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-stone-100/60 dark:hover:bg-stone-900/50 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-1 sm:gap-3 mb-1">
              <h4 class="font-serif text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 group-hover:text-accent-700 dark:group-hover:text-accent-400 transition-colors duration-300">Learning How Humans Learn to Play Board Games with GPT-4</h4>
              <span class="text-xs text-stone-400 dark:text-stone-500 whitespace-nowrap">AAAI Workshop 2024</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-500">Veronica Yeom-Song, Xinlei Lin, Ionatan Kuperwajs, Heiko Sch&uuml;tt, Wei Ji Ma, Luigi Acerbi</p>
          </article>

          <article class="group -mx-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-stone-100/60 dark:hover:bg-stone-900/50 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-1 sm:gap-3 mb-1">
              <h4 class="font-serif text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 group-hover:text-accent-700 dark:group-hover:text-accent-400 transition-colors duration-300">Comparing Machine and Human Learning in a Planning Task</h4>
              <span class="text-xs text-stone-400 dark:text-stone-500 whitespace-nowrap">CogSci 2022</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 mb-2">Zheyang Sam Zheng*, Xinlei Daisy Lin*, Jake Topping*, Wei Ji Ma</p>
            <a href="https://escholarship.org/uc/item/8wm748d8" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400 hover:text-accent-700 dark:hover:text-accent-300 transition-colors duration-300">
              Paper
              <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg>
            </a>
          </article>

          <article class="group -mx-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-stone-100/60 dark:hover:bg-stone-900/50 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-1 sm:gap-3 mb-1">
              <h4 class="font-serif text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 group-hover:text-accent-700 dark:group-hover:text-accent-400 transition-colors duration-300">Human Planning in Stochastic Environments</h4>
              <span class="text-xs text-stone-400 dark:text-stone-500 whitespace-nowrap">PsyArXiv 2025</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 mb-2">Jordan Lei, Jeroen Olieslagers, Nastaran Arfaei, Xinlei Lin, Wei Ji Ma</p>
            <a href="https://osf.io/bh56p" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400 hover:text-accent-700 dark:hover:text-accent-300 transition-colors duration-300">
              Paper
              <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg>
            </a>
          </article>

          <article class="group -mx-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-stone-100/60 dark:hover:bg-stone-900/50 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-1 sm:gap-3 mb-1">
              <h4 class="font-serif text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 group-hover:text-accent-700 dark:group-hover:text-accent-400 transition-colors duration-300">Complementary cortical and thalamic contributions to cell type&ndash;specific striatal activity dynamics during movement</h4>
              <span class="text-xs text-stone-400 dark:text-stone-500 whitespace-nowrap">Science Advances 2026</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 mb-2">Enida Gjoni, Ram Dyuthi Sristi, Haixin Liu, Shahar Dror, Xinlei Lin, Keelin O'Neil, Oscar M. Arroyo, Sun Woo Hong, Hannah Kim, Jeffrey Liu, Sonja Blumenstock, Byungkook Lim, Gal Mishne, Takaki Komiyama</p>
            <a href="https://www.science.org/doi/full/10.1126/sciadv.aea3935" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400 hover:text-accent-700 dark:hover:text-accent-300 transition-colors duration-300">
              Paper
              <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg>
            </a>
          </article>

        </div>

        <div class="mt-10">
          <a href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=PYIV3fcAAAAJ" target="_blank" class="text-sm text-stone-500 hover:text-stone-900 dark:hover:text-stone-200 link-underline transition-colors duration-300">
            All publications on Google Scholar
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Things that seem true to me right now -->
  <section class="py-20 border-t border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="section-label mb-10 reveal">Things that seem true to me right now</h2>

      <ul class="space-y-5 max-w-xl reveal delay-1">
        <li class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
          Women are controlled by hormones more than anyone talks about. Every week I'm a different person. It's the most underestimated battle.
        </li>
        <li class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
          After walking 46 miles in Patagonia &mdash; got sick on day 3, had to recover overnight and keep going &mdash; I realized the human body's potential is basically unlimited.
        </li>
        <li class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
          You can run a marathon untrained. I ran the NYC Marathon in 2024 with barely any training, finished in about 6 hours. You just have to trust yourself and vibe with the incredibly encouraging New Yorkers.
        </li>
        <li class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
          Everything in moderation is the best philosophy.
        </li>
        <li class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
          My entire PhD could be done in two months with the tools we have today. That's not a complaint &mdash; it's the most exciting thing about this moment.
        </li>
        <li class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
          Making something you can hold &mdash; ceramics, tiramisu &mdash; after months of only making things in code is satisfying in a way I can't fully explain.
        </li>
        <li class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
          Teaching my grandparents to use AI is the hardest product problem I've ever worked on.
        </li>
        <li class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
          The best skincare routine is sunscreen, sleep, and not worrying about it too much.
        </li>
        <li class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
          Tiramisu is the perfect dessert. I will not be taking questions.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section id="about" class="py-20 border-t border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="section-label mb-8 reveal">About</h2>

      <div class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 space-y-4 max-w-xl leading-relaxed reveal delay-1">
        <p>
          I snowboard when I can &mdash; Hokkaido is the dream &mdash; bake when I need to think, make ceramics, and am currently being managed by two cats named Boba and Milk who take their supervisory roles extremely seriously.
        </p>
        <p>
          People ask about my skincare routine more than my research, which I find extremely funny. Happy to talk about both.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <section id="contact" class="py-20 border-t border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="section-label mb-8 reveal">Contact</h2>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-8 text-sm reveal delay-1">
        <a href="mailto:leixlin@gmail.com" class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 hover:text-stone-900 dark:hover:text-stone-100 link-underline transition-colors duration-300">
          leixlin@gmail.com
        </a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/leixlin" target="_blank" class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 hover:text-stone-900 dark:hover:text-stone-100 link-underline transition-colors duration-300">
          Twitter
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/xinlei-lin-in" target="_blank" class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 hover:text-stone-900 dark:hover:text-stone-100 link-underline transition-colors duration-300">
          LinkedIn
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/daisilin" target="_blank" class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 hover:text-stone-900 dark:hover:text-stone-100 link-underline transition-colors duration-300">
          GitHub
        </a>
        <a href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=PYIV3fcAAAAJ" target="_blank" class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 hover:text-stone-900 dark:hover:text-stone-100 link-underline transition-colors duration-300">
          Google Scholar
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
